        "action": "Extend Sunday trading laws to also apply on Bank Holidays",
        "additional_details": "Bank Holidays should give everyone a break, including those who work in retail stores, especially when trading patterns appear to match those on a Sunday.",
        "background": "Retail stores and other relevant businesses should be made to follow Sunday trading laws on all public holidays in England, specifically being allowed to open for a maximum of 6 hours on these days. ",
